text: In case you missed our latest AMA for the :themes: themes challenge that happened last week, you can review it here! :slightly_smiling_face: <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gofL6tXmMXE&amp%3Bfeature=youtu.be>
For the HubSpot themes challenge, does a blog listing and blog post template count towards the 6 templates that need to be submitted with your theme?
